org.pipservices.commons.convert

Class FloatConverter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pipservices.commons.convert.FloatConverter

  • public class FloatConverter
extends Object
    Converts arbitrary values into float using extended conversion rules: - Strings are converted to float values - DateTime: total number of milliseconds since unix epo—Åh - Boolean: 1 for true and 0 for false

    ### Example ### 

     
 float value1 = FloatConverter.toNullableFloat("ABC"); // Result: null
 float value2 = FloatConverter.toNullableFloat("123.456"); // Result: 123.456
 float value3 = FloatConverter.toNullableFloat(true); // Result: 1
 float value4 = FloatConverter.toNullableFloat(new Date()); // Result: current milliseconds
